Surf_Nightmare
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Developed by:
razEr
Tilt
Silverlol
Junior
And thanks to Kratos for giving us this task.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This map was made for the Nightmare allround surf clan.

Visit their site at: www.nightmare-surf.com

This map is a njv version, and we won't make any jail versions of this map. There might be a final version if people request it.

The map is also the tryout map, which you have to pass in order to join nightmare's skill squad. (Minimum requirement)

All feedback is welcome, and on behalf of me and the all the other people involved in the making of this map, i say good luck & have fun! I hope you enjoy our map.

Yours sincerely, Razer.
